Kim Jong Il's Work Published in Indonesia 
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Pyongyang, April 5 (KCNA) -- Kim Jong Il's famous work "Kimilsungia Is an Immortal Flower which Came into Bloom in the Hearts of Humankind in the Era of Independence" was brought out in booklet in Indonesia on Mar. 31. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 This work came off the press on April 6, Juche 94 (2005).

Important Day in DPRK Observed in Ethiopia and Democratic Congo 
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Pyongyang, April 5 (KCNA) -- A seminar took place in Ethiopia and a reading session in Democratic Congo on Mar. 26 and 27 on the occasion of the 14th anniversary of Kim Jong Il's election as chairman of the DPRK National Defence Commission. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Nigatu Dagnachew, chairman of the Ethiopian Youth Study Group of the Juche Idea, at the seminar highly praised Kim Jong Il as the sun of the 21st century as he has led the human cause of independence to victory with his unique Songun leadership, adding that it has become a global trend to follow the Songun idea. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Bele Moukeleng, chairman of the Group for the Study of the Juche Idea of University of Kinshasa, at the reading session said that it is entirely thanks to the wise leadership of Kim Jong Il that socialist Korea has won one victory after another, frustrating the anti-DPRK moves of the imperialists. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Kamwiziku Octave, chairman of the National Committee for the Study of the Juche Idea of Democratic Congo, said that its followers would make positive efforts to know better about the true picture of the DPRK, in which the Juche idea has been embodied, and learn from it.

National Exhibition and Public Presentation of Machine Designs Held  
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Pyongyang, April 5 (KCNA) -- The 3rd national exhibition and public presentation of machine designs was held in Pyongyang under the sponsorship of the Central Committee of the Korean General Federation of Science and Technology. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Introduced there were achievements made in working out and materializing new designs to produce more machines as required by the IT age. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Drawing interest of the visitors were a design of new type machine and its general assembly plan developed in an indigenous way, various programs developed during computer-aided designing and achievements made in developing databases and modernizing information and technical means for designing. 
 Also introduced there were self-developed plotter and homepage and information on scientific and optimized designing.

S. Korean Organization Declares No to FTA  
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Pyongyang, April 5 (KCNA) -- The Headquarters of the All-People Movement for Checking south Korea-U.S. Free Trade Agreement reportedly held a press conference in a place near Chongwadae on April 2 at which it declared the results of the negotiations for the conclusion of FTA totally null and void. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 A press release read out at the conference said that the authorities hastily struck the deal on FTA with the U.S. in defiance of the desire of the people, stressing that it would wage a dynamic action to force the present pro-U.S. and undemocratic regime to step down. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 When the results of the negotiations are open to the public, the authorities' sycophancy and treachery will be brought into light, the press release pointed out, saying that the organization would intensify the movement for the total nullification of what was agreed upon at the negotiations, the prevention of its ratification at the "National Assembly" and the resignation of the "government".&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 For the present, it will hold candlelight cultural events and big rallies across south Korea in protest against the concluded FTA. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 More than 700 members of the headquarters held a candlelight cultural event that evening in protest against the south Korean authorities' humiliating behavior.

Anniversary of Chondoism Observed 
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Pyongyang, April 5 (KCNA) -- The "Heaven Day Ceremony" was held in Pyongyang Thursday to commemorate the 147th anniversary of the foundation of Chondoism. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Present there were Chairwoman Ryu Mi Yong, Advisor O Ik Je and officials of the Korean Chondoist Church Central Guidance Committee and Chondoists in Pyongyang. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Vice-chairman of the committee said in his speech at the ceremony that Chondoism, the indigenous religion of the Korean nation, enunciated such patriotic ideas as "Broad salvation of the people," "Paradise," "Rejection of West and Japan" and "Promotion of the National Interests and Welfare of the People" after its foundation and has since worked hard to materialize them for the past nearly one and half centuries. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 It is the long-standing desire and tradition of Chondoism, he added. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Noting that it is important to glorify the June 15 era of reunification by attaching importance to the nation, defending peace and achieving unity in order to accomplish the historic cause of national reunification, the cause of national historical significance, he said to do so is the only way of realizing the desire of Chondoism and means genuine patriotism. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The participants prayed for the withdrawal of the U.S. forces from south Korea and the earliest possible achievement of national reunification so that the desire of Chondoism can come true.

S. Korean Judicial Authorities' Fascist Action under Fire  
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Pyongyang, April 5 (KCNA) -- Some time ago, the south Korean judicial authorities imposed heavy punishment upon those related to the "case of Single-minded Association." This action was fascist tyranny against the DPRK and reunification as it is aimed at blocking national reconciliation and reunification. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Papers today observe this in signed commentaries carried in this regard. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The case cooked up in October last year was a sheer fabrication as it lacked clear evidence and those related to the case completely denied the charge, Rodong Sinmun notes, and goes on: &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The case is nothing but a charade orchestrated on the basis of a scenario worked out in a secret chamber of the Intelligence Service. This is clearly evidenced by the fact that those related to the case testified at the hearing that what they did was just the discussion they had on the issue of the reunification movement with the DPRK and the name of the "Single-minded Association" was the first words they heard while they were interrogated at the "Intelligence Service." &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The successive south Korean regimes fabricated big "spyring cases" to chill the warm desire of the people for reunification whenever the movement for achieving reunification through alliance with the north mounted in south Korea. But the reunification movement advanced and the truth behind the false cases was clearly probed. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The ultra-right conservative forces of the south Korean security authorities are clinging to dastardly methods to achieve their ulterior aim, but their cheap farce will get them nowhere. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Minju Joson in a signed commentary terms the recent action taken by the south Korean judicial authorities to punish people on false charge of espionage after fabricating the groundless case by linking them to the DPRK a deliberate and premeditated plot to deter the inter-Korean ties from warming up and bring back the era of confrontation.

Imperialists' Crafty Method for Domination Blasted 
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Pyongyang, April 5 (KCNA) -- A carrot approach being taken by the imperialists serves as a lever to carry out their appeasement strategy. This is a very crafty and wicked plot to create illusion about them by appeasing and deceiving their opponents in a bid to benumb their anti-imperialist spirit and completely disarm them ideologically and morally. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Rodong Sinmun Thursday observes this in a signed article. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 It goes on: &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The above-said approach may bring consequences as dangerous as open aggression by force of arms. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 One should not interpret the above-said approach as a sort of change in the aggressive nature of the imperialists. The carrot approach of the imperialists which is bound to be accompanied by appeasement tactics and smiling diplomacy is designed to do harm to their opponents at a slow pace till they prove ineffective in face of their moves for domination and end up collapsing. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 It is the aim sought by the imperialists in the above-said approach to create illusion about them and thus put other countries under the yoke of domination and subjugation and gratify their interests. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The imperialists, while acting an "apostle of peace" by abusing the wish of humankind for a peaceful free world, are craftily working to confuse the spirit of people and cause them to harbor illusion about imperialism. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 They are intensifying economic domination and subjugation of other countries by such levers as "aid", "cooperation" and "loan".&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 This is eloquently proved by the reality of those countries which have been put under the yoke of political subjugation after receiving the "aid" and "loan" offered by the imperialists as a "kind gesture." &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 There will be disastrous consequences for those countries which abandon their revolutionary principle and meet the imperialists' demand, taken in by glossy words uttered by them as part of their appeasement policy. Worse still, their wrong behavior may lead to the loss of their sovereignty. All countries should, therefore, be vigilant against the imperialists' carrot approach and should not be tempted by it under any circumstances.

Idea and Exploits of Kim Il Sung Lauded 
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Pyongyang, April 5 (KCNA) -- President Kim Il Sung performed undying feats by bringing about a dramatic turn in carving out the destiny of the country and the nation with his great idea and practical activities and making a new brilliant history of the victory of the cause of independence to be always recorded along with the history of the popular masses. His immortal exploits will shine forever. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Rodong Sinmun Thursday says this in a signed article. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 It goes on: &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The President is a peerlessly great man as he ushered in the era of independence and glorified it. He is the eternal sun of Juche as he indicated the way to be followed by the era with his brilliant ideological and theoretical wisdom and far-sightedness and performed immortal exploits in the struggle for accomplishing the popular masses' cause of independence through his total dedication and energetic leadership. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 This greatness lies in that he clearly indicated the way of achieving the victory of the popular masses' cause of independence by setting forth the Juche-oriented idea and line and set a brilliant example in carrying out their revolutionary cause despite the rigorous tempest of revolution. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 He founded the Juche idea and perfected it as the guiding idea in the era of independence in all fields and set forth the original idea and line of Songun in the practical struggle. The history of the struggle waged in the last century, inspired by his scientific guiding idea, clearly proved that the Juche idea and the Songun line serve as the main idea and line representing the present era. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The President steered the era and revolution without the slightest vacillation and hesitation, firmly convinced of the justice and victory of the above-said cause despite the worst adversity. His strong will, pluck and experienced and tested leadership ability have served as a fundamental source that enabled the servicepersons and people in the DPRK to achieve great victories and work miracles in the struggle for independence, sovereignty and socialism to startle the world. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The immortal revolutionary history of the President who ushered in the era of independence and steered it is brilliantly shining with his greatness. He is a world political elder and most outstanding great man as he ushered in the era of independence and glorified it with his great idea and practical activities, perfectly possessed of the personality as a great man to be acquired by a revolutionary leader and a statesman. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 His revolutionary history is the one of the popular leader as it is characterized by his total dedication to the popular masses' cause of independence and the one of an outstanding great man who carried out revolution and construction with his staunch revolutionary principle and creative ingenuity. It is the one of a peerlessly great man as it is characterized by extraordinary far-sightedness and optimism about future. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The era of independence which was started and led by the President is now making a dynamic advance under the leadership of Kim Jong Il. It is thanks to his guidance that the idea and exploits of the President will shine forever, the article concludes.

DPRK Representative Demands Stop to Suppression of Koreans in Japan
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Pyongyang, April 5 (KCNA) -- Japan should immediately stop its suppression of the General Association of Korean Residents in Japan (Chongryon) and Koreans in Japan and its discrimination against them. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 A DPRK representative demanded this, when discussing the report presented by a special rapporteur on opposing racism and national discrimination to the 4th meeting of the UN Human Rights Council on Mar. 28. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Recalling that the special rapporteur in his report took note of the fact that the Koreans in Japan, in particular, are subject to suppression and discrimination in Japan and proposed measures for putting an end to them, the DPRK representative said this was very important. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 He said that Japan has become brutal in its political suppression and human rights abuses against Chongryon and Koreans in Japan, something unprecedented since the formation of Chongryon. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Citing facts to prove Japan's frantic crackdown upon Chongryon, he noted that it mobilized heavily armed police forces to perpetrate an unreasonable search operation against at least 30 objects including the Headquarters and branches of Chongryon and Korean schools and indiscriminately arrest innocent people. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 He went on: &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 This reminds one of something that happens only in battlefields as it goes beyond the conception of suppression and discrimination. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 No wonder, political parties, organizations and media of different countries of the world termed Japan's suppression of Chongryon a gross violation of the publicly recognized international law and a crime against humanity. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 We request the special rapporteur to continue putting pressure upon the Japanese government till Japan puts an end to the suppression of Koreans in Japan and its national discrimination against them.

Periodicos denuncian represion fascista en el Sur de Corea
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Pyongyang, 5 de abril (ATCC) -- Los periodicos de este jueves, al denunciar la reciente represion de las autoridades judiciales del Sur de Corea que impusieron penas severas a los involucrados en el "caso de la sociedad Ilsim", la califican de fechoria  fascista contra la Republica Popular Democratica de Corea y de intento de obstaculizar la reconciliacion y la reunificacion de la nacion. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
  El comentario individual del diario Rodong Sinmun senala: &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
�@El caso en cuestion reportado en octubre del ano pasado es una pura invencion carente de pruebas claras que niegan totalmente los involucrados. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
  Es una farsa intrigante escenificada segun un guion elaborado en las camaras secretas del "Centro de informacion". Durante el juicio los involucrados en el "caso" declararon que ellos mismos habian consultado con el Norte de Corea sobre el movimiento por la reunificacion y que habian oido por primera vez el termino la "sociedad Ilsim" en el curso de la interrogacion del "centro de informacion".&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
  Historicamente, cada vez que en el Sur de Corea cobraba auge la tendencia por la reunificacion en alianza con el Norte, se fraguaron los "casos de grupos de espias" echando agua fria al anhelo de reunificacion de los habitantes. Pero, el movimiento por la reunificacion marchaba adelante y se esclarecieron los verdaderos aspectos de los casos inventados. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
  Con tal farsa grosera las fuerzas conservadoras ultraderechistas del Sur de Corea no podran convencer a nadie. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
  El periodico Minju Joson lo califica de una conspiracion de quienes tratan de impedir la mejora de las relaciones con el Norte y hacer retornarlas a la confrontacion.

Indonesia: obra de Kim Jong Il en folleto 
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Pyongyang, 5 de abril (ATCC) -- Una Empresa de Edicion e Imprenta de Indonesia dio a luz el 31 de marzo en folleto la obra maestra del Dirigente Kim Jong Il "La Kimilsungia es la flor inmarcesible brotada en el alma de la humanidad de la epoca de independencia".&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
�@Esta obra fue publicada el 6 de abril del 94 (2005) de la Era Juche.
